1
00:00:24,030 --> 00:00:25,290
[Adapted from a novel published on
Qidian Reading under China Literature]

2
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:27,180
["Way of Choices" by Mao Ni]

3
00:00:28,300 --> 00:00:29,830
[Minors]

4
00:00:29,860 --> 00:00:31,550
[should watch with guardian consent]

5
00:02:14,230 --> 00:02:19,370
[Way of Choices]

6
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:24,600
[Previously]

7
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,250
The third round of combat match

8
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:24,440
officially

9
00:02:24,730 --> 00:02:25,920
begins!

10
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:28,520
In the combat match of the Imperial Court
Exam, fighters are randomly paired.

11
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:30,840
The Seven Prodigies are awfully powerful.

12
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:32,200
If we meet them…

13
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,840
I'm not afraid to fight them.

14
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,370
I'm just afraid that if I lose,

15
00:02:35,370 --> 00:02:37,170
I'll bring shame to our academy.

16
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:38,070
[Three Moves In One, Red God]

17
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:39,920
Although the journey ahead is hard,

18
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:41,300
I never think about it.

19
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:43,000
Only by focusing on moving forward

20
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,130
and trying your best

21
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,690
will there be a miracle.

22
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:48,240
That will

23
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,440
is very good.

24
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:50,960
Chen Changsheng,

25
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:53,440
I'm looking forward to it.

26
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:06,520
The Demon Race is coming in force
this time.

27
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:08,250
It'll be another tough battle.

28
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,680
These nuisances keep coming
one after another.

29
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,680
I can't kill them all.

30
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,400
It's okay.

31
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,830
I'm here.

32
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:16,520
Recover your strength as soon as possible.

33
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:24,680
Qi Jian!

34
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,160
Senior!

35
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:39,120
Protecting juniors is a senior's duty.

36
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:42,400
Feibai,

37
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:44,180
you stole the limelight.

38
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,640
Of the Divine Nation's Seven Prodigies,

39
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:46,840
not one of us can fall.

40
00:03:49,850 --> 00:03:51,250
We live and die together;

41
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:53,170
advance and retreat together!

42
00:03:55,079 --> 00:03:56,480
That was too ruthless.

43
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:58,120
Since the Imperial Court Exam began,

44
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,840
I've never seen anyone so badly injured.

45
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:00,840
Senior.

46
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:06,360
Wofu Zhexiu!

47
00:04:07,810 --> 00:04:09,980
[Wofu Zhexiu]

48
00:04:09,990 --> 00:04:11,760
[Episode 12]

49
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:15,840
The Imperial Court Exam is meant
to be a display of restraint.

50
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,769
Yet, you striked with such malice!

51
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:24,300
The first round of combat matches ends!

52
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:26,480
The top eight winners are:

53
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:29,000
Gou Hanshi of Lishan Sword Sect,

54
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:30,720
Qi Jian,

55
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:33,240
Wofu Zhexiu of the Fifth College of Shendu,

56
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,280
Sima Lv,

57
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:36,840
Ye Xiaolian of Cijian Temple.

58
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:39,400
Chen Changsheng
of the State Religious Academy,

59
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:40,480
Bai Luoheng,

60
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:42,440
Tang Thirty-Six!

61
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:43,080
Director!

62
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:44,040
Master!

63
00:04:44,080 --> 00:04:45,440
Come on!

64
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:48,560
Let's wait and see

65
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:51,880
who among you will become emerge
as the winner

66
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:54,120
of this Imperial Court Exam!

67
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:57,520
The second round of combat matches

68
00:04:57,520 --> 00:04:59,120
begins!

69
00:04:58,409 --> 00:04:59,830
[Forest Battlefield]

70
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:11,200
Wofu Zhexiu!

71
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:19,080
You injured my senior.

72
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,650
I want you to pay for it!

73
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:34,400
I'm sorry.

74
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,810
I really need money.

75
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:36,930
So,

76
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,120
I must win.

77
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,280
Money?

78
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:41,960
Just for that?

79
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:43,920
You bastard!

80
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:47,560
What?

81
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,130
He won so easily?

82
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:50,320
Who is he?

83
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:51,840
Wofu Zhexiu!

84
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,840
He once killed countless Demons
in the snowfield.

85
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:55,320
His military achievements are remarkable!

86
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,680
They say he has madness.

87
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,440
When it flares up, he's terrifying.

88
00:05:58,440 --> 00:06:00,500
That's why he's called Crazy Zhexiu.

89
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:03,100
No one dares to get involved with him.

90
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:05,180
This is bad.

91
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:08,080
If he becomes the director's opponent,

92
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,280
that'll be trouble.

93
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,340
[Lakeside Battlefield]

94
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:18,720
Next time,

95
00:06:18,930 --> 00:06:20,530
don't push yourself so hard.

96
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,380
This is a combat match!

97
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:25,440
They're not fighting,

98
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:27,240
they're just tending to wounds,

99
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:29,340
and even eating cakes?

100
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:30,400
Foul!

101
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,720
Who says you can't eat cakes?

102
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,780
Are you jealous or something?

103
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:35,480
You...

104
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:39,380
Please, examiner, make a ruling.

105
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:43,360
I've checked all the rules.

106
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:44,240
Indeed,

107
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,480
it doesn't say you can't eat cakes.

108
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,380
This is strange.

109
00:06:46,380 --> 00:06:48,360
It's the first time
in Imperial Court Exam history.

110
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:50,680
I want to eat Princess Luo's cakes too.

111
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:55,040
You're so badly injured.

112
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,000
Looks like I'm lucky.

113
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,320
I got an easy win.

114
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:02,680
What?

115
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,520
Compared to Liang Banhu,

116
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,200
you're far inferior.

117
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:12,240
I concede.

118
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:13,920
Junior Ye,

119
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,330
thank you for the match.

120
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:19,560
The second round of the combat matches
ended surprisingly fast.

121
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:22,160
The top four winners are:

122
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:23,640
the State Religious Academy's

123
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:25,440
Chen Changsheng,

124
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,920
Tang Thirty-Six,

125
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,480
the Lishan Sword Sect's

126
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,000
Gou Hanshi,

127
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:35,090
and Zhaixing Academy's

128
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:38,120
Wofu Zhexiu!

129
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:40,520
Among these people,

130
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:42,400
you started cultivation the latest.

131
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:45,659
Body Baptized in Dragon's Blood
can only take you this far.

132
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,240
From here on,

133
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:49,920
whether you can defeat these geniuses

134
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,840
depends on you.

135
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:56,520
The fight for first place draws near.

136
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:58,700
The third round of the combat matches

137
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,240
begins!

138
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:05,880
Will it be you?

139
00:08:07,130 --> 00:08:08,850
[Third Round of Combat Matches]

140
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:29,680
Just what I was worried about.

141
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,040
Who are you worried about?

142
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,039
Thirty-Six?

143
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:35,840
Your injuries

144
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:36,980
are severe.

145
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,830
Worry about yourself first.

146
00:08:40,330 --> 00:08:42,280
Why is everyone
from the State Religious Academy

147
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,640
so stubborn?

148
00:08:43,919 --> 00:08:44,740
[Eternal Night]

149
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,540
Stop with the smoke and mirrors.

150
00:08:46,540 --> 00:08:48,060
Show some real spirit!

151
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,280
Watch closely.

152
00:08:49,610 --> 00:08:51,810
This new sword technique I just learned

153
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:54,830
[Three Moves In One: Red God]

154
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:53,220
will dazzle you blind!

155
00:09:00,790 --> 00:09:01,940
Break it

156
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,030
for me!

157
00:09:02,610 --> 00:09:03,500
[Break]

158
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,760
You actually broke my Eternal Night.

159
00:09:05,760 --> 00:09:07,420
This move is indeed powerful.

160
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:10,680
Foolish.

161
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:12,240
Among this batch,

162
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,880
only Qiushan Jun

163
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:15,440
can defeat Gou Hanshi.

164
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:24,520
That sword

165
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:26,980
was excellent.

166
00:09:39,280 --> 00:09:40,470
I concede.

167
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,560
Actually that sword just now

168
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:54,530
was the last of my True Essence.

169
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:55,860
It was cool, right?

170
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:58,520
You're quite an interesting one.

171
00:09:58,520 --> 00:09:59,440
Of course.

172
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,560
I can't beat you anyway.

173
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:03,480
But giving it my all

174
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:05,720
I can still drain
some of your True Essence.

175
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:06,480
Gou Hanshi.

176
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:07,920
Your last opponent

177
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:10,280
will surely be Chen Changsheng.

178
00:10:12,860 --> 00:10:16,020
[Bamboo Forest Battlefield]

179
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:19,760
Many people

180
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,640
are betting against you.

181
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:22,760
So?

182
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:24,760
I...

183
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:26,680
really need money.

184
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:35,540
Did you join the Imperial Court Exam
just to make money?

185
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,320
Yes.

186
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,320
I want money.

187
00:10:40,300 --> 00:10:41,950
A lot of money.

188
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:42,350
[Destiny Star: Shadow Moon]

189
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,160
Mystic Frost!

190
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,630
Body Baptized in Dragon's Blood
gave me greater

191
00:10:59,630 --> 00:11:01,400
speed and strength
than others of the same realm.

192
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:03,200
Yet, his demonization keeps up.

193
00:11:05,070 --> 00:11:06,400
He is indeed something.

194
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:23,160
Damn it.

195
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:24,570
Here it comes again!

196
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:25,540
Strange.

197
00:11:25,620 --> 00:11:26,880
What's wrong with him?

198
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,320
Take this!

199
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:40,920
If I didn't use dragon breath
and Seated Illumination together to suppress him,

200
00:11:40,920 --> 00:11:42,320
this would be difficult.

201
00:11:47,570 --> 00:11:48,390
This is...

202
00:11:48,800 --> 00:11:50,520
It's starting again!

203
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:53,940
Run!

204
00:11:57,520 --> 00:11:58,680
Otherwise...

205
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,040
It won't stop

206
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,440
until one of us dies.

207
00:12:08,920 --> 00:12:10,310
[Blood Surge, Bloodlust Metamorphosis]

208
00:12:11,220 --> 00:12:13,230
I've long heard
that this wolf cub goes mad

209
00:12:13,230 --> 00:12:14,650
when he loses his mind.

210
00:12:15,310 --> 00:12:17,400
His True Essence increases
by several times.

211
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:18,580
He's like a god of slaughter.

212
00:12:18,580 --> 00:12:19,920
Last time he went mad,

213
00:12:19,940 --> 00:12:23,320
he killed hundreds of demons in a battle.

214
00:12:23,340 --> 00:12:24,560
Chen Changsheng

215
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:26,220
will definitely lose.

216
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:45,720
Take this!

217
00:12:51,520 --> 00:12:52,920
My meridians are broken.

218
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:54,320
I can only burn True Essence Snowy Plains

219
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:56,640
to mimic Seated Illumination
and gain a fleeting surge of True Essence.

220
00:12:56,640 --> 00:13:00,280
But if I use it continuously, I risk
getting consumed by starfire.

221
00:13:00,280 --> 00:13:01,540
I must quickly find out

222
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:03,540
why he suddenly went berserk.

223
00:13:13,700 --> 00:13:15,130
[Shadow Wolves' Sudden Attack]

224
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:22,360
Looks like the outcome is decided.

225
00:13:36,170 --> 00:13:37,300
Strange heartbeat.

226
00:13:37,370 --> 00:13:38,320
Excessive demonization.

227
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:39,040
The meridians are reversed.

228
00:13:39,040 --> 00:13:39,980
Heartbeat.

229
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,020
Heartbeat!

230
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:41,840
That's it!

231
00:13:42,040 --> 00:13:44,260
The 12 innate meridians govern the mind.

232
00:13:44,260 --> 00:13:44,860
An anomaly

233
00:13:45,160 --> 00:13:46,760
has one extra hidden channel.

234
00:13:46,760 --> 00:13:48,160
Blood surges like tides.

235
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:50,660
When the tide rises,
the spirit becomes unstable.

236
00:13:50,660 --> 00:13:51,940
[Soul Loss Syndrome]

237
00:13:50,760 --> 00:13:52,560
It's called Soul Loss Syndrome.

238
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:54,100
So this isn't a technique.

239
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:55,490
It's a disease!

240
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:56,960
When it happens,
the heart feels like knives

241
00:13:56,960 --> 00:13:57,960
and it's worse than death.

242
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,820
Yet he managed to hold on till now!

243
00:14:05,370 --> 00:14:07,300
Golden needle to anchor the pulse.

244
00:14:10,160 --> 00:14:11,080
Begin at the Ghost Palace,

245
00:14:10,690 --> 00:14:11,360
[Ghost Palace]

246
00:14:14,170 --> 00:14:16,460
Trying to restrain a berserk Zhexiu?

247
00:14:17,160 --> 00:14:19,120
Wishful thinking!

248
00:14:20,680 --> 00:14:21,560
then move to the Ghost Trust.

249
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:21,730
[Ghost Trust]

250
00:14:22,670 --> 00:14:23,600
Ghost Fortress.

251
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:27,170
Ghost Heart.

252
00:14:27,800 --> 00:14:28,400
No.

253
00:14:28,640 --> 00:14:29,660
What is he doing?

254
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:32,760
It's the Thirteen Ghost Needles.

255
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,920
Wasn't the Thirteen Ghost Needles

256
00:14:34,920 --> 00:14:36,600
lost 200 years ago?

257
00:14:37,560 --> 00:14:38,800
How could a young man

258
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:40,830
master such a needle technique?

259
00:14:40,860 --> 00:14:41,590
Ghost Cave.

260
00:14:41,870 --> 00:14:42,640
Ghost Hall.

261
00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:44,500
Ghost Pillow.

262
00:14:44,900 --> 00:14:45,700
Ghost Hidden!

263
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:48,010
Ghost Minister.

264
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:49,080
Ghost Bed.

265
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,040
Ghost Market.

266
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:51,520
Ghost Spring!

267
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:52,980
Temper them with fire

268
00:14:52,980 --> 00:14:54,320
to anchor the soul and settle the spirit.

269
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:55,270
Ghost Seal!

270
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:13,160
That Wofu boy is having
another one of his fits again.

271
00:15:13,160 --> 00:15:14,420
Quick, get the chains!

272
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:17,500
Such a young child with this
strange illness.

273
00:15:17,500 --> 00:15:18,620
What a sin!

274
00:15:19,280 --> 00:15:20,880
Forget about the compensation

275
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:22,340
from Zhexiu's mother.

276
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:24,280
The child is pitiful.

277
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:26,320
Keep an eye on this monster.

278
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:28,250
Don't let him go out to harm others!

279
00:15:36,320 --> 00:15:38,700
His madness is too rare.

280
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:41,450
We can only give him some harsh medicine.

281
00:15:41,520 --> 00:15:42,480
But

282
00:15:42,560 --> 00:15:44,290
the cost of these medicines...

283
00:15:51,640 --> 00:15:52,320
Mother.

284
00:15:53,040 --> 00:15:53,960
Don't worry.

285
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:56,380
I can fight the demons

286
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:57,940
and earn military merits.

287
00:15:58,760 --> 00:16:01,250
I'll pay off the family's debts

288
00:16:01,520 --> 00:16:02,980
and the medical expenses!

289
00:16:31,160 --> 00:16:31,820
It's okay now.

290
00:16:31,820 --> 00:16:32,480
Relax.

291
00:16:33,160 --> 00:16:34,270
Control your breathing.

292
00:16:34,270 --> 00:16:35,270
Steady your mind.

293
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:48,960
You...

294
00:16:50,440 --> 00:16:53,280
You can turn me back to normal?

295
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:55,640
Your meridians are abnormal

296
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:57,440
so you can’t control your power.

297
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:59,280
I guess you didn’t mean to

298
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:01,460
severely injure Guan Feibai either.

299
00:17:02,800 --> 00:17:03,600
Why are you...

300
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:04,920
helping me?

301
00:17:05,359 --> 00:17:07,359
When you went mad, you told me to run.

302
00:17:07,599 --> 00:17:08,460
So I helped you.

303
00:17:10,880 --> 00:17:11,599
Please.

304
00:17:12,040 --> 00:17:12,640
Help me

305
00:17:13,040 --> 00:17:14,319
cure my illness.

306
00:17:19,520 --> 00:17:22,520
Chen Changsheng
defeated Zhexiu in this way?

307
00:17:22,520 --> 00:17:22,980
This...

308
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:23,460
This...

309
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:25,079
How is that possible?

310
00:17:25,240 --> 00:17:26,200
He's well-versed in all the Scriptures

311
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:27,319
and cultivated rapidly.

312
00:17:27,319 --> 00:17:28,880
He even has great medical skills.

313
00:17:28,880 --> 00:17:31,480
Such a genius hasn't appeared
in hundreds of years.

314
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:34,280
Worth of being
the Grand Pontiff's chosen junior.

315
00:17:34,280 --> 00:17:35,880
He always brings surprises.

316
00:17:38,600 --> 00:17:39,400
Moon Bear,

317
00:17:39,560 --> 00:17:40,890
you're still alive too?

318
00:17:44,530 --> 00:17:46,250
You look more hurt than me.

319
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:50,440
Why didn't Gou Hanshi stab you mute?

320
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:53,650
Chen Changsheng
of the State Religious Academy.

321
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:56,400
Gou Hanshi of Lishan Sword Sect.

322
00:17:58,720 --> 00:18:00,380
Congratulations to you both.

323
00:18:00,400 --> 00:18:01,200
You advance

324
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:04,720
to the final battle!

325
00:18:05,200 --> 00:18:06,640
The fight for first place

326
00:18:07,080 --> 00:18:10,360
in the Imperial Court Exam

327
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:14,060
[Imperial Court Exam Final Battle]

328
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:18,240
begins!

329
00:18:21,670 --> 00:18:25,180
[To be continued]

330
00:18:26,710 --> 00:18:28,400
Follow Way of Choices animation.

331
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:29,800
Light up your Destiny Star.

332
00:18:29,800 --> 00:18:31,730
We hope you all follow your heart.

333
00:18:33,740 --> 00:18:37,010
[In the next episode]

334
00:18:33,800 --> 00:18:35,160
In front of Weiyang Palace

335
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:36,560
we agreed to fight again.

336
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:38,050
Now, you've done it.

337
00:18:39,080 --> 00:18:39,780
But

338
00:18:40,220 --> 00:18:41,680
if you seek quick success,

339
00:18:41,840 --> 00:18:43,240
you'll only lose faster.

340
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:44,850
Give up.

341
00:18:45,560 --> 00:18:47,760
The gap between our realms is too great.

342
00:18:52,840 --> 00:18:53,920
I have no way back.

343
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:55,960
So even if I wear shoes,

344
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:58,480
I'm still just a barefoot boy.

